
Component:	GUI
Description: 	Handles the display of every interaction within the student app
Stereotype:	Component
Required interfaces:	none
Provided interfaces:	Booking, payment, login and events list


Component:	Cloud connection manager
Description: 	This component handles authorisation within the app from the user
Stereotype:	Component
Required interfaces:	login
Provided interfaces:	login


Component:	Book event
Description: 	This component runs within the app to handle the booking of students to events
Stereotype:	Component
Required interfaces:	Booking
Provided interfaces:	Booking

Component:	Find event
Description: 	This component is used to find the events that have been searched by the user.
Stereotype:	Component
Required interfaces:	Event list
Provided interfaces:	Event list

Component:	payments
Description: 	This component is used by the user to buy tickets that they are booking for 
Stereotype:	Component 
Required interfaces:	Payment
Provided interfaces:	Process payment, verify payment


Component:	Booking manager
Description: 	This gives the necessary forms for the user to fill out to book onto the event
