Required interfaces:	booking
Provided interfaces:	Authentication

Component:	Payment manager
Description: 	This component checks the payment that the user has sent 
Stereotype:	Component 
Required interfaces:	Process payment, verify payment
Provided interfaces:	Authentication

Component:	Event data
